header.gameNote: AIR FORCE RESERVE JERRY COLANGELO CLASSIC

videos.description: Gonzaga big man Brandon Clarke drives baseline and puts in the nice up-and-under layup.
videos.headline: Gonzaga's Clarke converts sweet layup

videos.description: Gonzaga forward Corey Kispert gets the pass from Josh Perkins and knocks down a 3-pointer in the corner.
videos.headline: Kispert drains 3 to extend Zags' lead

videos.description: Tennessee guard Jordan Bowden hits the big time jumper over the defender giving Tennessee the lead at the half.
videos.headline: Tennessee's Bowden knocks down jumper at the end of the half

videos.description: Yves Pons goes tries to dunk but he is quickly blocked by Gonzaga big man Brandon Clarke.
videos.headline: Gonzaga's Clarke says NO with big block

videos.description: Tennessee's Admiral Schofield knocks down the 3, which is immediately followed by Gonzaga's Zach Norvell Jr. hitting a 3.
videos.headline: Schofield and Norvell trade 3-pointers

videos.description: Tennessee's Admiral Schofield banks in the 3-pointer from the top of the key to give Tennessee the lead late in the game.
videos.headline: Schofield banks in 3 to give Tennessee lead

videos.description: Admiral Schofield's 3-pointer late in the fourth quarter is the difference for Tennessee as it defeats top-ranked Gonzaga.
videos.headline: Schofield's go-ahead 3 knocks off No. 1 Gonzaga

videos.description: Admiral Schofield was on fire and knocked down six 3-pointers, including the game winner to help Tennessee to victory.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCB Highlight (Schofield hits 6 threes in upset of No. 1 Gonzaga) 2018/12/09 ESHEET

videos.headline: Schofield hits six 3s in upset of No. 1 Gonzaga
